                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://vlog.xuite.net/vlog/guest/basic.php?media_id=T0U5VUpyLTE2MTQzMjkuZmx2">Red Bamboo Ratsnake in the wild (Wulai, North Taiwan)</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
