                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://blog.sina.com.tw/d100vs/article.php?pbgid=30839&entryid=168369">Juvenile Red Bamboo Ratsnake in the wild</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://blog.sina.com.tw/d100vs/article.php?pbgid=30839&entryid=587201">Various Red Bamboo Ratsnakes in the wild</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://blog.sina.com.tw/d100vs/article.php?pbgid=30839&entryid=589413">More Red Bamboo Ratsnakes in the wild</a></li>
                    </ul>     
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
