                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.fieldherpforum.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=372">Red Bamboo Ratsnake</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.fieldherpforum.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=2187">Orange-Red Bamboo Ratsnake</a></li>
